Comment: 0,0:01:37.91,0:01:39.66,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,Good morning, everyone!
Comment: 0,0:01:40.41,0:01:41.99,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,It's a beautiful day!
Comment: 0,0:01:45.33,0:01:47.21,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,Huh? Takako?
Comment: 0,0:01:50.46,0:01:53.42,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,What? It's four in the morning...
Comment: 0,0:01:53.42,0:01:56.13,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,The early bird catches the worm!
Comment: 0,0:01:56.51,0:01:59.93,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,Not only do you have your\N regular duties at the inn to take care of,
Comment: 0,0:01:59.93,0:02:02.64,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,you also have to help with the preparations for our wedding!
Comment: 0,0:02:03.01,0:02:05.52,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,Thus, I've concluded that cutting the sleeping time
Comment: 0,0:02:05.52,0:02:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,of you, young ones, will be the\N first step to making this a success.
Comment: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:10.86,Default,Both,0,0,0,,What?
Comment: 0,0:02:10.86,0:02:14.78,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,Anyway, you now have a\N meeting with Enishing you must attend.
Comment: 0,0:02:14.78,0:02:17.53,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,Here we go, to the staff dining room!
Comment: 0,0:02:21.32,0:02:25.41,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I wonder why Takako's so fired up suddenly.
Comment: 0,0:02:38.84,0:02:41.72,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,Good morning, Ms. Tomoe!
Comment: 0,0:02:42.09,0:02:44.97,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,Let's begin a wonderful day!
Comment: 0,0:02:46.22,0:02:47.14,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,Hey!
Comment: 0,0:02:47.48,0:02:49.06,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Oh... sorry.
Comment: 0,0:02:49.56,0:02:51.77,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,Come on, have a seat like everyone else, Ms. Tomoe.
Comment: 0,0:02:51.77,0:02:53.56,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,We'll now begin the meeting.
Comment: 0,0:02:53.56,0:02:54.90,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,Let's get fired up!
Comment: 0,0:02:54.90,0:02:56.65,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,Are you ready?
Comment: 0,0:02:57.23,0:03:03.66,Default,Teach,0,0,0,,Anyway, what led Ryunosuke\N Akutagawa to write {\i1}Rashomon{\i0}?
Comment: 0,0:03:03.66,0:03:05.24,Default,Teach,0,0,0,,His wedding with Yayoi Yoshida,
Comment: 0,0:03:05.24,0:03:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,a girl he'd known since he\N was a child, had been called off...
Comment: 0,0:03:09.50,0:03:12.04,Default,Teach,0,0,0,,Hey!
Comment: 0,0:03:12.04,0:03:13.58,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Oh... I'm sorry!
Comment: 0,0:03:13.58,0:03:15.84,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,It never rings, so I...
Comment: 0,0:03:15.84,0:03:17.84,Default,Teach,0,0,0,,Huh? What about your boyfriend?
Comment: 0,0:03:19.26,0:03:22.64,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Now's not a good time to bring up stuff like—
Comment: 0,0:03:28.10,0:03:29.48,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Comment: 0,0:03:30.35,0:03:32.14,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,What were you thinking?!
Comment: 0,0:03:32.14,0:03:34.98,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I can't believe you called me in the middle of class.
Comment: 0,0:03:34.98,0:03:36.36,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sorry, sorry.
Comment: 0,0:03:36.65,0:03:40.19,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,I just have this image of you constantly at work.
Comment: 0,0:03:40.19,0:03:42.66,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,I forgot that you're a high schooler.
Comment: 0,0:03:43.57,0:03:45.49,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,So, what do you need?
Comment: 0,0:03:45.49,0:03:48.49,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, I received an invitation.
Comment: 0,0:03:48.49,0:03:50.16,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,{\i1}Enishi's getting married, huh?
Comment: 0,0:03:50.16,0:03:51.46,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Comment: 0,0:03:51.46,0:03:53.12,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're coming, right?
Comment: 0,0:03:53.58,0:03:55.13,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,It isn't that simple.
Comment: 0,0:03:55.13,0:03:57.34,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,{\i1}What? You're busy with work?
Comment: 0,0:03:57.34,0:03:59.09,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,I've got a lot to take care of.
Comment: 0,0:03:59.09,0:04:00.80,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,I'll send him a congratulatory message, though.
Comment: 0,0:04:01.34,0:04:03.63,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Enishi, huh...
Comment: 0,0:04:04.72,0:04:06.80,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,He's streaked ahead of you, huh?
Comment: 0,0:04:06.80,0:04:08.01,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hush.
Comment: 0,0:04:10.18,0:04:13.98,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Hey, your relationships with your\N boyfriends don't last very long, do they?
Comment: 0,0:04:14.31,0:04:15.23,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,{\i1}What?
Comment: 0,0:04:15.69,0:04:18.94,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,What does it mean to you\N when you go out with someone?
Comment: 0,0:04:18.94,0:04:22.49,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,{\i1}What? You've gone and\N caught yourself another boyfriend?
Comment: 0,0:04:22.49,0:04:24.45,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,N-No!
Comment: 0,0:04:25.66,0:04:26.53,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hmm...{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:04:26.99,0:04:30.16,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe it's because I still have a one-sided crush on your father.
Comment: 0,0:04:30.41,0:04:31.50,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,What?!
Comment: 0,0:04:31.50,0:04:32.91,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,A one-sided crush?!
Comment: 0,0:04:35.96,0:04:37.59,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,You didn't have to scream at me.
Comment: 0,0:04:37.59,0:04:39.88,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,I thought I said something nice for a change.
Comment: 0,0:04:40.17,0:04:42.13,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,A one-sided crush?!
Comment: 0,0:04:42.13,0:04:46.55,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I didn't expect those words from my sex crazed mother.
Comment: 0,0:04:46.55,0:04:47.64,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,{\i1}Jeez...
Comment: 0,0:04:47.89,0:04:52.68,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to find a new love\N because I can't forget my old one.
Comment: 0,0:04:52.68,0:04:54.81,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,{\i1}I couldn't get anything out of that love.
Comment: 0,0:04:56.23,0:04:59.23,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,But, well, it's been 15 years since your father died.
Comment: 0,0:05:00.61,0:05:04.78,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Recently, I've been thinking that\N maybe I don't need to get anything out of it.
Comment: 0,0:05:04.78,0:05:05.99,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why not?
Comment: 0,0:05:05.99,0:05:09.87,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,It's once in a lifetime that you\N meet someone you love so much.
Comment: 0,0:05:10.62,0:05:13.33,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Maybe the fact that I met him was lucky in itself.
Comment: 0,0:05:14.96,0:05:15.75,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Huh?
Comment: 0,0:05:15.75,0:05:16.62,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Ohana?
Comment: 0,0:05:17.54,0:05:18.38,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,What?
Comment: 0,0:05:28.39,0:05:31.31,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hearing her talk about her one-sided crush made my heart beat so fast!
Comment: 0,0:05:31.31,0:05:32.77,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,{\i1}Jeez!
Comment: 0,0:05:33.89,0:05:35.35,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,One-sided crush?
Comment: 0,0:05:41.19,0:05:42.40,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why...
Comment: 0,0:05:43.23,0:05:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why did I try to forget about Ko?
Comment: 0,0:05:49.78,0:05:53.33,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,{\i1}Minchi is so serious about Tohru...
Comment: 0,0:06:00.13,0:06:05.34,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why did I think I couldn't have a one-sided crush on him?
Comment: 0,0:06:11.10,0:06:13.81,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Okay, it's done!
Comment: 0,0:06:14.10,0:06:15.72,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Wow! Amazing!
Comment: 0,0:06:15.72,0:06:16.81,Default,Yuina,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Comment: 0,0:06:17.06,0:06:20.06,Default,Yuina,0,0,0,,It's not bad for an amateur's work.
Comment: 0,0:06:20.06,0:06:22.69,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,All that's left is for someone to try it on,\N so we can make some minor adjustments.
Comment: 0,0:06:22.69,0:06:24.07,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Could you try it on, Yuina?
