Comment: 0,0:07:02.27,0:07:05.61,Default,Yuina,0,0,0,,She may not be as... big as Takako there,
Comment: 0,0:07:05.86,0:07:08.53,Default,Yuina,0,0,0,,but as long as hers aren't bigger, she can try it on!
Comment: 0,0:07:08.53,0:07:11.86,Default,Yuina,0,0,0,,As long as hers aren't bigger!
