Comment: 0,0:07:38.85,0:07:39.56,Default,Renji,0,0,0,,Huh?
Comment: 0,0:07:39.93,0:07:42.94,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,I noticed that you have to be hard on them when they're in a slump,
Comment: 0,0:07:43.77,0:07:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,in order for them to overcome it.
