Comment: 0,0:08:26.02,0:08:30.48,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I don't mind that you dislike me, but we made that dress
Comment: 0,0:08:30.48,0:08:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,together with Yuina for Takako\N and the young master's wedding!
Comment: 0,0:08:35.28,0:08:36.82,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,We worked really hard on it!
Comment: 0,0:08:37.37,0:08:38.62,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,How could you—
Comment: 0,0:08:38.62,0:08:39.41,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Comment: 0,0:08:39.41,0:08:40.83,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,"Worked really hard"?
Comment: 0,0:08:41.12,0:08:42.79,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,So has Tohru!
