Comment: 0,0:08:56.80,0:08:58.55,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I'm going to be direct like you, Minchi!
Comment: 0,0:08:58.55,0:08:59.97,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,So I'm—
Comment: 0,0:09:01.10,0:09:02.27,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,Cut the crap!
Comment: 0,0:09:02.60,0:09:04.48,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,Die!
Comment: 0,0:09:04.48,0:09:06.65,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,Why do you have a crush?!
