Comment: 0,0:09:07.90,0:09:09.73,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,Die! Die! Die!
Comment: 0,0:09:09.73,0:09:10.48,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,No!
Comment: 0,0:09:10.48,0:09:12.36,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,If I die, I won't be able to go out with anyone!
