Comment: 0,0:09:18.53,0:09:19.66,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,Why?!
Comment: 0,0:09:19.66,0:09:21.83,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,He's just some loser!
Comment: 0,0:09:21.83,0:09:24.16,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,You've never even seen him!
Comment: 0,0:09:25.37,0:09:28.08,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,Anyone's a loser compared to Tohru!
Comment: 0,0:09:28.08,0:09:32.05,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,Tohru's so handsome! He's perfect!
Comment: 0,0:09:32.05,0:09:34.01,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Both of you, stop already!
Comment: 0,0:09:39.30,0:09:41.56,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,Minko, you...
Comment: 0,0:09:46.52,0:09:47.77,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Wait, Minchi!
Comment: 0,0:10:18.26,0:10:20.01,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,What are you? Stupid?
Comment: 0,0:10:20.01,0:10:20.89,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,What?
Comment: 0,0:10:21.72,0:10:26.93,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,Well... you're right. I'm kind of interested in Ohana.
Comment: 0,0:10:28.77,0:10:31.94,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,Perhaps I do like her.
Comment: 0,0:10:32.65,0:10:35.65,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,But it's not like I want to do anything.
Comment: 0,0:10:35.65,0:10:38.70,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,I just get excited watching her,
Comment: 0,0:10:39.32,0:10:42.66,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,trying to imagine what kind of crazy stunt she'll pull next.
Comment: 0,0:10:45.04,0:10:49.54,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,On the other hand, you keep me in great suspense.
Comment: 0,0:10:52.50,0:10:53.42,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,H-Hey...
Comment: 0,0:10:53.42,0:10:56.17,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,Sorry, did I just say something awful?!
Comment: 0,0:10:56.17,0:10:58.30,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,No... No, it's just...
Comment: 0,0:10:59.09,0:11:00.22,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,I'm happy...
Comment: 0,0:11:01.26,0:11:09.10,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,You're willing to watch over me without even liking me...
Comment: 0,0:11:15.48,0:11:18.74,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,You really are stupid, aren't you?
Comment: 0,0:11:25.12,0:11:26.45,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,I've got most of the dirt off.
Comment: 0,0:11:29.20,0:11:30.58,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Ohana!
Comment: 0,0:11:31.58,0:11:33.29,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Comment: 0,0:11:33.29,0:11:34.63,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,I was really moved!
Comment: 0,0:11:35.88,0:11:40.80,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,I've never been in love before,
Comment: 0,0:11:40.80,0:11:43.59,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,but I thought what you said was wonderful.
Comment: 0,0:11:43.84,0:11:45.47,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Wonderful?
Comment: 0,0:11:45.47,0:11:48.47,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Yeah, about continuing your crush.
Comment: 0,0:11:49.56,0:11:55.81,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Fighting isn't nice, but I think both of you are wonderful.
Comment: 0,0:11:56.77,0:11:59.36,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,You're both able to love someone so much.
Comment: 0,0:11:59.36,0:12:01.11,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,I'm so moved!
Comment: 0,0:12:01.57,0:12:02.82,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Nakochi...
Comment: 0,0:12:03.53,0:12:05.32,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "I'm moved"?
Comment: 0,0:12:08.74,0:12:09.95,Default,Both,0,0,0,,Minchi!
Comment: 0,0:12:12.37,0:12:13.25,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Okay.
Comment: 0,0:12:16.88,0:12:19.84,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Wow! It looks great on you!
Comment: 0,0:12:21.88,0:12:25.34,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Hey, we should get her to hold some white flowers!
Comment: 0,0:12:26.60,0:12:28.14,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I've seen it on TV!
Comment: 0,0:12:28.14,0:12:29.64,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,It's supposed to make it more appealing, right?
Comment: 0,0:12:29.89,0:12:33.73,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,I'll borrow the flowers by the staircase!
Comment: 0,0:12:34.10,0:12:35.56,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,N-Nakochi?
Comment: 0,0:12:41.90,0:12:43.70,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Is your nose okay?
Comment: 0,0:12:45.16,0:12:47.66,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, absolutely.
Comment: 0,0:12:47.66,0:12:48.66,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,See—
Comment: 0,0:12:48.99,0:12:49.74,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,What?
Comment: 0,0:12:50.49,0:12:52.50,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,I'm not giving up.
Comment: 0,0:12:53.37,0:12:58.09,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,A-As in you're going to try and\N force me to go out with Tohru?
Comment: 0,0:12:58.09,0:12:59.34,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,No!
Comment: 0,0:12:59.84,0:13:00.96,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,I...
Comment: 0,0:13:00.96,0:13:03.51,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,I want to go out with him, so...
Comment: 0,0:13:04.68,0:13:06.22,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,I'm not going to give that up.
Comment: 0,0:13:07.59,0:13:11.43,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,I want to go out with him, so\N I'm going to continue my crush.
Comment: 0,0:13:11.85,0:13:12.98,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Minchi...
Comment: 0,0:13:13.27,0:13:17.94,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,I'm going to be direct like you said, so...
Comment: 0,0:13:23.49,0:13:24.74,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,{\i1}Balut!
Comment: 0,0:13:27.66,0:13:30.58,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,O-Ohana? Did you two fight ag—
Comment: 0,0:13:31.08,0:13:34.00,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,"Balut" is back!
Comment: 0,0:13:35.71,0:13:40.84,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,{\i1}And after that, the preparations for the wedding went smoothly.
Comment: 0,0:13:42.46,0:13:45.42,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,{\i1}I sort of decided...
Comment: 0,0:13:46.05,0:13:50.05,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,{\i1}that I'd confess to Ko after the wedding.
Comment: 0,0:13:54.18,0:13:56.69,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Wow, amazing!
Comment: 0,0:13:56.69,0:13:57.60,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,Perfect!
Comment: 0,0:13:58.10,0:14:00.61,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,You decorated in even the smallest of places!
Comment: 0,0:14:02.07,0:14:04.32,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Thanks. I have the feeling that this will
Comment: 0,0:14:02.23,0:14:04.23,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,{\an8}Thank you so much! {overlap}
Comment: 0,0:14:04.32,0:14:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,be a wonderful wedding thanks to you all.
Comment: 0,0:14:04.82,0:14:06.57,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,{\an8}This is wonderful! {overlap}
Comment: 0,0:14:06.95,0:14:08.82,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I think so too!
Comment: 0,0:14:15.50,0:14:17.46,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Minchi, this way!
Comment: 0,0:14:18.25,0:14:19.29,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Please excuse us!
Comment: 0,0:14:26.63,0:14:28.47,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,You're so pretty, Takako...
Comment: 0,0:14:28.72,0:14:30.47,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,Of course!
Comment: 0,0:14:30.47,0:14:34.97,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,This is the day a woman looks the prettiest in her life!
Comment: 0,0:14:35.35,0:14:38.35,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,In a woman's life...
Comment: 0,0:14:38.73,0:14:41.06,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,I have a favor to ask you.
Comment: 0,0:14:41.06,0:14:42.36,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,About the bouquet toss...
Comment: 0,0:14:44.07,0:14:45.19,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,All right!
Comment: 0,0:14:48.74,0:14:50.91,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,I haven't seen you since college.
Comment: 0,0:14:51.37,0:14:52.91,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,When did you start dating Takako?
Comment: 0,0:14:52.91,0:14:54.20,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,W-Well...
Comment: 0,0:14:58.87,0:15:02.42,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,We've become bride and groom on this day,
Comment: 0,0:15:02.42,0:15:07.51,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,and we're so happy to be able to\N announce this to you all this afternoon.
Comment: 0,0:15:08.26,0:15:13.47,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,We swear to work together as a married couple,
Comment: 0,0:15:13.76,0:15:17.68,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,and to start up a warm, happy family.
Comment: 0,0:15:34.20,0:15:37.12,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,Okay, bring it on!
Comment: 0,0:15:49.51,0:15:51.26,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,The wedding ceremony's over!
Comment: 0,0:15:51.26,0:15:53.05,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,Now we're in a race against time!
Comment: 0,0:15:53.05,0:15:54.01,Default,All,0,0,0,,Okay!
Comment: 0,0:16:01.73,0:16:03.44,Default,Yuina,0,0,0,,What should I do...
Comment: 0,0:16:03.44,0:16:05.77,Default,Yuina,0,0,0,,I'm nervous about being the master of ceremonies...
Comment: 0,0:16:05.77,0:16:07.77,Default,Yuina,0,0,0,,Hey, Oshimizu,
Comment: 0,0:16:07.77,0:16:10.82,Default,Yuina,0,0,0,,does my hair look fine? Is it weird?
Comment: 0,0:16:11.28,0:16:13.41,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,It looks fine! Later!
Comment: 0,0:16:18.20,0:16:21.46,Default,Yuina,0,0,0,,Oshimizu looks so nice when she's hustling!
Comment: 0,0:16:21.79,0:16:24.08,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,A kitchen is a battlefield! Let's go!
Comment: 0,0:16:24.08,0:16:24.96,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,Phải, sir!
Comment: 0,0:16:24.96,0:16:26.04,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,Good!
Comment: 0,0:16:26.04,0:16:27.71,Default,Renji,0,0,0,,Tohru, give me some orders.
Comment: 0,0:16:27.71,0:16:28.38,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,Huh?
Comment: 0,0:16:28.71,0:16:31.01,Default,Renji,0,0,0,,You're in charge today.
Comment: 0,0:16:32.05,0:16:33.01,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,Okay!
Comment: 0,0:16:33.01,0:16:35.76,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,Could you parboil those vegetables,
Comment: 0,0:16:35.76,0:16:37.01,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,descale the carp,
Comment: 0,0:16:37.01,0:16:37.85,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,fry those,
Comment: 0,0:16:37.85,0:16:40.10,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,and decorate the dishes with the cucumbers?
Comment: 0,0:16:40.81,0:16:42.98,Default,Renji,0,0,0,,Th-That's quite a lot of work.
Comment: 0,0:16:43.98,0:16:47.86,Default,Yuina,0,0,0,,Okay, I'd like to read the congratulatory greetings now.
Comment: 0,0:16:48.23,0:16:52.36,Default,Yuina,0,0,0,,This is from the groom's older sister, Matsumae Satsuki.
Comment: 0,0:16:52.36,0:16:55.66,Default,Yuina,0,0,0,,"They always say that a relationship gets better after a stormy fight,"
Comment: 0,0:16:55.66,0:16:57.95,Default,Yuina,0,0,0,,"but I'm not sure what the weather is like today."
Comment: 0,0:16:58.70,0:17:03.04,Default,Yuina,0,0,0,,"Either way, you need to make sure she's wet, all right?"
Comment: 0,0:17:04.25,0:17:05.75,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Oh, Mom...
Comment: 0,0:17:07.21,0:17:09.13,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,What about the next dish?
Comment: 0,0:17:10.00,0:17:11.38,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,The previous one was the last of them.
Comment: 0,0:17:13.17,0:17:14.59,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,Great work today, everyone!
Comment: 0,0:17:15.22,0:17:16.72,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Invitations?
Comment: 0,0:17:16.72,0:17:20.85,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,We're invited to the wedding too!
Comment: 0,0:17:23.31,0:17:25.14,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,You look so pretty, Takako.
Comment: 0,0:17:25.14,0:17:26.31,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Comment: 0,0:17:29.31,0:17:31.94,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Wow, these are all so delicious!
Comment: 0,0:17:32.73,0:17:35.82,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,It's the first time I've tasted Tohru's cooking like this.
Comment: 0,0:17:36.95,0:17:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Comment: 0,0:17:38.99,0:17:41.95,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,Sorry... I couldn't stop him from doing this.
Comment: 0,0:17:42.62,0:17:45.46,Default,Yuina,0,0,0,,So, for our next performance...
Comment: 0,0:17:47.08,0:17:48.79,Default,Jiro,0,0,0,,Where art thou?!
Comment: 0,0:17:50.29,0:17:52.92,Default,Jiro,0,0,0,,Oh, where art thou, my destined love!
Comment: 0,0:17:54.46,0:17:56.34,Default,Jiro,0,0,0,,There you are!
Comment: 0,0:17:56.63,0:17:59.47,Default,Jiro,0,0,0,,My beloved... Takako!
Comment: 0,0:18:03.89,0:18:05.56,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,Wh-What in the world?!
Comment: 0,0:18:05.89,0:18:08.44,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,Now, for the baiser amor!
Comment: 0,0:18:09.10,0:18:10.11,Default,Bean,0,0,0,,W—
Comment: 0,0:18:10.11,0:18:10.94,Default,Bean,0,0,0,,Wait—
Comment: 0,0:18:14.57,0:18:16.32,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,Don't react, or you'll lose.
Comment: 2,0:19:22.34,0:19:27.10,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,I didn't help out with this wedding at all.
Comment: 2,0:19:27.56,0:19:33.27,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,But these two, and the young workers at Kissui Inn,
Comment: 2,0:19:33.27,0:19:35.73,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,have created such an incredible ceremony.
Comment: 2,0:19:36.52,0:19:38.82,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,I apologize for boring you with stories of my past,
Comment: 2,0:19:39.40,0:19:44.37,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,but 40 years ago, I created Kissui Inn\N with my late husband, and with Denroku...
Comment: 2,0:19:44.37,0:19:48.91,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,No, with Mr. Denroku.
Comment: 2,0:19:49.91,0:19:52.29,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,That's what it means to be young.
Comment: 2,0:19:52.29,0:19:58.30,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,Even if you stumble and get lost,\N you challenge yourself to new things.
Comment: 2,0:19:58.76,0:20:01.88,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,You'll be able to create something new.
Comment: 2,0:20:03.76,0:20:07.81,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,I look forward to seeing the new things these two,
Comment: 2,0:20:07.81,0:20:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and the rest of Kissui Inn create,
Comment: 2,0:20:09.93,0:20:15.31,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,while I'll sit back and enjoy my tea from the far distance.
Comment: 2,0:20:18.27,0:20:20.24,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Everyone's future?
Comment: 2,0:20:20.24,0:20:22.36,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,Watching from afar?
Comment: 0,0:22:15.98,0:22:18.02,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,It ended without any troubles.
Comment: 0,0:22:18.52,0:22:19.35,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Comment: 0,0:22:20.90,0:22:22.98,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,Looks like everything's just about cleaned up.
Comment: 0,0:22:24.94,0:22:25.94,Default,Renji,0,0,0,,Madam Manager,
Comment: 0,0:22:27.07,0:22:31.12,Default,Renji,0,0,0,,about that speech you gave earlier...
Comment: 0,0:22:37.75,0:22:41.04,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,The reason why I asked you all here...
Comment: 0,0:22:43.04,0:22:46.97,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,is because Mr. Denroku told me the other day...
Comment: 0,0:22:48.22,0:22:49.18,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,This...
Comment: 0,0:22:49.80,0:22:57.60,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,that he wanted someone to succeed the logs he kept for over 40 years.
Comment: 0,0:22:59.44,0:23:03.23,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,Does that mean you're quitting Kissui Inn, Beanman?!
Comment: 0,0:23:04.73,0:23:06.48,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,But, why?
Comment: 0,0:23:06.48,0:23:11.49,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,These logs are like a history book of Kissui Inn.
Comment: 0,0:23:11.49,0:23:15.45,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,The tears, the laughs... everything is written in here.
Comment: 0,0:23:15.45,0:23:18.20,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,Look how worn it is.
Comment: 0,0:23:21.37,0:23:24.88,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,I'm thinking about sealing\N Kissui Inn, along with these logs,
Comment: 0,0:23:24.88,0:23:27.80,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,after the Bonbori festival this year.
Comment: 0,0:23:31.76,0:23:32.51,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,You going to see him?
Comment: 0,0:23:32.51,0:23:32.93,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,What?
Comment: 0,0:23:32.93,0:23:34.10,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Your crush.
Comment: 0,0:23:34.30,0:23:35.01,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Oh...
Comment: 0,0:23:35.01,0:23:38.27,Default,Bean,0,0,0,,A man is responsible for waiting patiently.
Comment: 3,0:23:38.27,0:23:41.39,Default,Ko,0,0,0,,Ohana, you're nothing like a bland coffee.
